text: Val-Revermont is a commune in the Ain department of eastern France. It was established on January 1, 2016. It is made of the former communes of Treffort- Cuisiat and Pressiat.Arrêté préfectoral 4 December 2015 == Related pages == *Communes of the Ain department == References == Category:2016 establishments in France
title: Val-Revermont
